 "cells": [
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Project 90 \\u2014 Local Multimodal Research Notebook\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Combine text + image evidence in one answer flow \\u2014 fully local.**\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Component | Choice |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"|-----------|--------|\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| VLM | Ollama (minicpm-v / llava) |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| LLM | Ollama (qwen3:8b) |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Embeddings | nomic-embed-text |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Vector Store | ChromaDB |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Interface | Jupyter |\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 1 \\u00b7 What You Will Learn\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"1. Build a **multimodal evidence pipeline** (text + images)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"2. Use **VLM** for image analysis and **LLM** for text analysis\\n\",\n",
    "    \"3. **Merge evidence** from multiple modalities into a single answer\\n\",\n",
    "    \"4. Handle **VLM fallback** gracefully\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 2 \\u00b7 Why It Matters\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Real-world research involves both text documents and visual evidence.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"A multimodal pipeline lets you query across both simultaneously.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 3 \\u00b7 Setup\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# !pip install -q langchain langchain-ollama langchain-community chromadb langchain-text-splitters Pillow matplotlib\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 4 \\u00b7 Imports\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"import json, base64, shutil\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from pathlib import Path\\n\",\n",
    "    \"import matplotlib\\n\",\n",
    "    \"matplotlib.use('Agg')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_ollama import ChatOllama, OllamaEmbeddings\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.documents import Document\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.prompts import ChatPromptTemplate\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.output_parsers import StrOutputParser\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.messages import HumanMessage\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_community.vectorstores import Chroma\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_text_splitters import RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"MODEL = 'qwen3:8b'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"VLM_MODEL = 'minicpm-v'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"llm = ChatOllama(model=MODEL, temperature=0.1)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"embeddings = OllamaEmbeddings(model='nomic-embed-text')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"try:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vlm = ChatOllama(model=VLM_MODEL, temperature=0.3)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vlm.invoke('test')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    USE_VLM = True\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f'VLM: {VLM_MODEL}, LLM: {MODEL}')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"except:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    USE_VLM = False\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vlm = llm\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f'VLM unavailable, text-only mode. LLM: {MODEL}')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 5 \\u00b7 Create Multimodal Evidence\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"We create both text documents and chart images as evidence sources.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Text evidence\\n\",\n",
    "    \"text_docs = [\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    'Q4 2024 Revenue Report: Total revenue was $2.3M, up 15% quarter-over-quarter. SaaS subscriptions contributed 65%, consulting 25%, training 10%.',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    'Customer Growth: Active customers reached 450, a 12% increase. Enterprise segment grew fastest at 25%. Churn rate improved to 2.1% from 3.4%.',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    'Product Milestones: API v3 launched with 3x throughput. Mobile app 2.0 released. AI assistant entered beta with 50 pilot users.',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    'Market Analysis: Mid-market competition intensified. Three new entrants priced 20% below. Our differentiation is enterprise features and support SLA.',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Chart evidence\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Path('evidence').mkdir(exist_ok=True)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"months = ['Jul','Aug','Sep','Oct','Nov','Dec']\\n\",\n",
    "    \"revs = [1.6, 1.7, 1.8, 1.9, 2.1, 2.3]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(6,3))\\n\",\n",
    "    \"ax.plot(months, revs, 'b-o')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"ax.set_title('H2 2024 Monthly Revenue ($M)')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"ax.set_ylabel('Revenue')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"fig.savefig('evidence/revenue_chart.png', dpi=100, bbox_inches='tight')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"plt.close()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f'{len(text_docs)} text docs, 1 chart image')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 6 \\u00b7 Build Text Index\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"docs = [Document(page_content=t, metadata={'source': f'doc_{i}', 'type': 'text'}) for i, t in enumerate(text_docs)]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"splitter = RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter(chunk_size=200, chunk_overlap=30)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"chunks = splitter.split_documents(docs)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"shutil.rmtree('chroma_multimodal', ignore_errors=True)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"store = Chroma.from_documents(chunks, embeddings, persist_directory='chroma_multimodal')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"retriever = store.as_retriever(search_kwargs={'k': 3})\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f'Indexed {len(chunks)} text chunks')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 7 \\u00b7 Multimodal Query Pipeline\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"def multimodal_query(question):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    # Step 1: Retrieve text evidence\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    text_results = retriever.invoke(question)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    text_context = '\\\\n'.join([f'[{d.metadata[\\\"source\\\"]}] {d.page_content}' for d in text_results])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\n\",\n",
    "    \"    # Step 2: Get image evidence (if VLM available)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    image_insight = ''\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    chart_path = 'evidence/revenue_chart.png'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    if USE_VLM and Path(chart_path).exists():\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        with open(chart_path, 'rb') as f:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            b64 = base64.b64encode(f.read()).decode()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        msg = HumanMessage(content=[\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            {'type': 'text', 'text': f'Based on this chart, answer: {question}'},\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            {'type': 'image_url', 'image_url': f'data:image/png;base64,{b64}'},\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        ])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        image_insight = vlm.invoke([msg]).content\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    else:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        # Fallback: use chart data description\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        chart_desc = f'Revenue chart shows H2 2024: {dict(zip(months, revs))}'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        image_insight = (ChatPromptTemplate.from_messages([\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            ('system', 'Analyze this chart data to help answer the question.'),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            ('human', 'Chart: {data}\\\\nQuestion: {q}'),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        ]) | llm | StrOutputParser()).invoke({'data': chart_desc, 'q': question})\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\n\",\n",
    "    \"    # Step 3: Merge evidence\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    merge_prompt = ChatPromptTemplate.from_messages([\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        ('system', 'Combine text and visual evidence to answer the question. Cite sources.'),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        ('human', 'Question: {question}\\\\n\\\\nText Evidence:\\\\n{text}\\\\n\\\\nVisual Evidence:\\\\n{image}'),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    return (merge_prompt | llm | StrOutputParser()).invoke({\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        'question': question, 'text': text_context, 'image': image_insight\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    })\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print('Pipeline ready.')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 8 \\u00b7 Run Queries\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"QUESTIONS = [\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    'What was the revenue trend in H2 2024?',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    'How is the competitive landscape changing?',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    'What are the key product achievements?',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for q in QUESTIONS:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f'\\\\nQ: {q}')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    answer = multimodal_query(q)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f'A: {answer[:300]}')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 9 \\u00b7 Export\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"results = [{'question': q, 'answer': multimodal_query(q)} for q in QUESTIONS]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"with open('multimodal_results.json', 'w') as f: json.dump(results, f, indent=2, default=str)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print('Saved.')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 10 \\u00b7 Key Takeaways\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Multimodal RAG combines text retrieval + VLM image analysis\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Evidence merging produces richer, more grounded answers\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Text fallback ensures functionality without VLM hardware\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Production: index images with captions for better retrieval\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  }\n",
    " ],\n",
